    {
      "bookmarkId": "35008156_1_2717-2790",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "2717-2790",
      "markText": "四海听到这里，十分感慨，这吃的问题，非得着实解决不可，他发誓将来长大了，要努力工作赚钱，想吃多少，就能吃多少，直至吃饱为止，是，这肯定是他的宏愿。",
      "totalCount": 308,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35008156&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2717&rangeEnd=2790",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fbc3233072162e9cfbc8e79?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=2717&rangeEnd=2790"
