    {
      "bookmarkId": "35008156_7_1383-1459",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1383-1459",
      "markText": "“在平地上，”庞英杰告诉他，“二千个工人不停操作，一日一夜间，铁路可推进廿五哩，同样的工程，白人要做七日七夜，可是白人每日工资一元半，我们只拿一块钱！”",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35008156&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1383&rangeEnd=1459",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fbc3233072162e9cfbc8e79?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1383&rangeEnd=1459"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35008156_3_1488-1533",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1488-1533",
      "markText": "“发疯，这就叫你难过了？告诉你，罗少爷，这不止是个人骑人的世界，这还是个人吃人的世界呢。”",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35008156&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1488&rangeEnd=1533",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fbc3233072162e9cfbc8e79?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1488&rangeEnd=1533"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "35008156_6_2159-2210",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2159-2210",
      "markText": "人体构造肯定有问题，怎么搞的，一天到晚，吃完又吃，吃完再吃，成日就是吃，民以食为天，都不用干别的事了。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35008156&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2159&rangeEnd=2210",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fbc3233072162e9cfbc8e79?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2159&rangeEnd=2210"
    },
    {
