      "markText": "四海不脱小生意人本色，他乘搭商船回去，不但不用买票，且有薪酬，是，他又拿起锅铲，在厨房做帮工，罗四海的算盘实在十分精密。",
      "totalCount": 270,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=35008156&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4411&rangeEnd=4471",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/fbc3233072162e9cfbc8e79?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=4411&rangeEnd=4471"
    },
